  "description": "Cinda Securities Co., Ltd. engages in the securities brokerage, investment banking, and asset management businesses in China and internationally. The company offers agency trading services for stocks, funds, warrants, and bonds; and personalized investment advisory and consulting services. It also provides equity and bond financing and financial advisory services, such as IPOs, listed company refinancing, corporate and enterprise bonds, financial bonds, asset-backed securities, mergers and acquisitions, and listing recommendations. In addition, the company offers targeted (single) and collective asset management, asset securitization, and asset management investment advisory services. Further, it engages in the private equity investment fund, alternative investment, research, and other businesses. The company was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Beijing, China. Cinda Securities Co., Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of China Cinda Asset Management Co., Ltd.",
